    <description><![CDATA[
ProofStack is a comprehensive digital evidence assessment platform that helps legal professionals evaluate the admissibility of digital evidence against established legal standards.

## Features
- Progressive Enhancement API Key Management
- Zero barrier to entry with demo mode
- AI-powered legal analysis with Gemini integration
- Secure local API key storage
- Educational content and mock analysis
- SQLite database for evidence storage
- Professional menu system with keyboard shortcuts
- Chain of custody tracking
- Legal analysis results storage

## Usage
After installation, launch ProofStack from the Start Menu or desktop shortcut. The application works immediately in demo mode, or add your Gemini API key for AI-powered analysis.

## Requirements
- Windows 10 or later
- 200 MB free disk space
- Internet connection for AI features (optional)
]]></description>
